# AhaDiff Agent

Use AhaDiff after code changes to produce verified learn-back artifacts.

Preferred commands:

- `ahadiff learn HEAD~1..HEAD`
- `ahadiff learn --staged`
- `ahadiff quiz <run_id>`
- `ahadiff review`
- `ahadiff verify <run_id>`

Do not commit local provider credentials or private audit logs.
